Calcul des distances¶

In [2]:
Copied! 
from cpge import PriorityQueue

def dijkstra(G, s):
    n = len(G)
    dist = n*[float("inf")]
    dist[s] = 0
    q = PriorityQueue()
    for v in range(n):
        q.add(v, dist[v])

    while not q.is_empty():
        u = q.take_min()
        for v in range(n):
            d = dist[u] + G[u][v]
            if v in q and d < dist[v]:
                q.update(v, d)
                dist[v] = d
    return dist


dijkstra(G, 0)
from cpge import PriorityQueue def dijkstra(G, s): n = len(G) dist = n*[float("inf")] dist[s] = 0 q = PriorityQueue() for v in range(n): q.add(v, dist[v]) while not q.is_empty(): u = q.take_min() for v in range(n): d = dist[u] + G[u][v] if v in q and d < dist[v]: q.update(v, d) dist[v] = d return dist dijkstra(G, 0)
